WEBVTT

00:03:58.593 --> 00:04:01.331
Dia akan bermediasi
dengan lingkungan kita,

00:04:01.331 --> 00:04:02.906
dan akan berkata sesuatu seperti,

00:04:02.906 --> 00:04:04.271
"Jadi, saya sudah cek.

00:04:04.295 --> 00:04:06.955
Kita sekarang di konferensi TEDx ...

00:04:06.979 --> 00:04:09.909
(Tawa)

00:04:11.083 --> 00:04:12.625
(Tepuk tangan)

00:04:13.378 --> 00:04:14.168
Gas?

00:04:14.422 --> 00:04:16.638
Mungkin, kalau kamu duduk di tepi,

00:04:16.638 --> 00:04:17.575
dan kamu tahu,

00:04:18.375 --> 00:04:20.225
kamu bisa mengeluarkannya pelan-pelan.

00:04:20.225 --> 00:04:22.065
(Tawa)

00:04:22.089 --> 00:04:23.248
Tapi padat --

00:04:23.272 --> 00:04:24.473
mungkin nanti."

00:04:24.497 --> 00:04:25.940
(Tawa)

00:04:25.964 --> 00:04:31.394
